        <p><span class="highlight">Red Rover</span> is an experimental game about space exploration and the human voyage to Mars.  It combines elements of first-person discovery and puzzle-solving -- seen in game such as <span class="highlight">Myst</span> and <span class="highlight">Proteus</span> -- with an abstract and contemplative approach to hard sci-fi -- as in <span class="highlight">2001: A Space Odyssey</span> or Carl Sagan's <span class="highlight">Cosmos: A Personal Voyage.</span> Out in 2013 for PC, Mac, and Linux.</p>
